So of course this Wien's displacement law

36
00:03:26,019 --> 00:03:30,930
which gives the position of the maximum
of the black body peak as a function of temperature

37
00:03:30,930 --> 00:03:36,660
can be expressed in wavelengths or in frequencies.
depending on whether we express the luminance

38
00:03:36,660 --> 00:03:40,209
as a funtion of wavelength
or frequency.

39
