Another feature which will interest us,

46
00:04:37,700 --> 00:04:42,880
is of course the total energy, the energy
flux density

47
00:04:42,880 --> 00:04:46,630
developed by a stellar object which radiates
black body radiation,

48
00:04:46,630 --> 00:04:51,620
in other words the whole of the luminance
at all wavelengths

49
00:04:51,620 --> 00:04:55,550
or at all frequencies.
So once the integration is done the available

50
00:04:55,550 --> 00:04:58,670
energy
once we have integrated the black body for

