00:05:04,760 --> 00:05:15,890
of the energy flux which is simply
proportional to the temperature to the fourth.

53
00:05:15,890 --> 00:05:19,760
So we have here a proportionality constant
which is of course a power

54
00:05:19,760 --> 00:05:22,620
