The luminosity, is here the total energy freed

60
00:05:51,990 --> 00:05:57,810
by the star,
The luminosity will be given in erg/s.

61
00:05:57,810 --> 00:06:07,130
This luminosity, will be the surface of the
star multiplied by M.

62
00:06:07,130 --> 00:06:18,880
So 4π r² * σ T^4, where we have here the
